 {"id":"bd-35wf","title":"Research: Post-2025-10 tiny CPU reranker model discovery","description":"## Goal
Build an *exhaustive* candidate list of **tiny, CPU-only rerankers released or updated after 2025-10-31**. This list is the **sole source of truth** for the reranker bake-off (new models only).

## Hard Filters (non-negotiable)
- Release/update date >= 2025-11-01 (`createdAt` + `lastModified`)
- CPU-only viable (ONNX/gguf/int8 or native CPU runtime)
- “Tiny” footprint: prefer <= 500M params or <= 500MB disk (quantized OK)
- Open weights or locally runnable (API-only models **ineligible**)
- License permits local inference

## Discovery Workflow (exhaustive)
### 0) Web scan for post-2025-10 announcements
- Scan vendor blogs, HF blog, and reranker release notes for tiny CPU rerankers
- Capture candidate names + release dates + CPU benchmarks
- Reconcile against HF API sweep; note any missing or API-only models

### 1) Hugging Face Hub API sweep
- Filters: `text-ranking`, `cross-encoder`, `reranker`
- Sort by `lastModified desc`, paginate via `Link` header
- Capture: `modelId`, dates, tags, file list, license

